---
const lastUpdated = "February 13, 2026";
const protocolID = "TOS-REF-0992";
---
    <main class="pt-32 lg:pt-48 pb-24">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
            
            <div class="border-b-2 border-black pb-12 mb-16">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
                    <span class="font-mono text-[#A53029] text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.5em]">// Protocol_ID: {protocolID}</span>
                    <div class="h-[1px] w-12 bg-gray-200"></div>
                </div>
                <h1 class="font-heading text-6xl lg:text-8xl uppercase tracking-tighter leading-none mb-8">
                    Terms of <span class="italic text-transparent stroke-black">Service</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400">
                    Effective Date: {lastUpdated} // Version: 2.0.4
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="prose prose-zinc max-w-none 
                prose-h2:font-heading prose-h2:uppercase prose-h2:text-3xl prose-h2:tracking-tight prose-h2:mt-16 prose-h2:mb-8
                prose-p:font-sans prose-p:text-gray-600 prose-p:leading-relaxed prose-p:mb-6
                prose-strong:text-black">
                
                <p class="lead text-xl text-black font-medium italic border-l-4 border-[#A53029] pl-6 my-10">
                    By accessing the Global Music Solutions (GMS) interface, you agree to comply with the following operational parameters. Please review these terms carefully.
                </p>

                <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
                <p>
                    By engaging with this website or our backend services, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these protocols, access to the GMS system is denied.
                </p>

                <h2>2. Service Scope // Scope of Work</h2>
                <p>
                    GMS provides technical administration for the music industry. Our services include, but are not limited to:
                </p>
                <ul class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-tight text-gray-500 space-y-2 mb-6">
                    <li>[01] Royalty Stream Verification</li>
                    <li>[02] Global Cue Sheet Processing</li>
                    <li>[03] Technical Metadata Auditing</li>
                    <li>[04] Administrative Backend Support</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>3. Intellectual Property</h2>
                <p>
                    All content, logos, proprietary methodologies, and code (the "Assets") displayed on this site are the exclusive property of Global Music Solutions. Unauthorized reproduction, extraction, or "scraping" of these assets is strictly prohibited.
                </p>

                <h2>4. User Responsibilities</h2>
                <p>
                    Users are responsible for ensuring the accuracy of any metadata or information provided to GMS for processing. GMS is not liable for data loss resulting from incorrect user input or third-party transmission failures.
                </p>

                <h2>5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
                <p>
                    In no event shall GMS be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our digital archive or administration tools. We provide our "Liner Notes" and data insights for informational purposes only.
                </p>

                <h2>6. Termination of Access</h2>
                <p>
                    We reserve the right to terminate or suspend access to our terminal immediately, without prior notice, for any breach of these Terms or for maintenance of system integrity.
                </p>

                <div class="mt-24 pt-12 border-t border-gray-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-8">
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase text-gray-400 mb-2">Governing Jurisdiction</p>
                        <p class="font-heading text-xl uppercase tracking-tight">International Copyright Law</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-right">
                        <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase text-gray-400 mb-2">Support Terminal</p>
                        <p class="font-sans text-sm">legal@globalmusicsolutions.com</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="py-12 border-t border-gray-100 text-center">
        <p class="font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-300">
            Global Music Solutions // Legal Operations Dept.
        </p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>

<style is:global>
    :root {
        --font-heading: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
        --font-sans: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }
    .font-heading { font-family: var(--font-heading); }
    .font-sans { font-family: var(--font-sans); }
    .font-mono { font-family: var(--font-mono); }
    .stroke-black { -webkit-text-stroke: 1.5px black; }
</style>